@startuml act_calc_payroll
!theme plain
title Activity Diagram: Automated Payroll Calculation Flow

|Manager|
start
:Trigger Payroll Calculation\n(Select Month/Year);

|System (Salary Service)|
:Fetch Standard Work Days\n(Exclude Sundays & Holidays);

|Database (PostgreSQL)|
:Query Active Users;
:Query Attendance Logs;
:Query Approved Leaves;
:Query Settings (Penalties);

|System (Salary Service)|
while (More Users?) is (Yes)
  if (Is Payroll already PAID?) then (Yes)
    :Skip User;
  else (No)
    :Aggregate Logs & Leaves for the Month;
    :Calculate Total Work Days;
    :Calculate Late/Early Penalties;
    :Calculate Unexcused Absence Penalties;
    :Compute Final Net Salary;
    :UPSERT to `monthly_payrolls`\n(Status: DRAFT);
  endif
endwhile (No)

|Manager|
:View Draft Payroll Table UI;
stop
@enduml